Patti Clare https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Patti_Clare 0 Patti Clare (born 3 March 1976) is an English actress, best known for playing the character of Mary Taylor in the ITV soap opera Coronation Street since 2008. She is a three-time winner of the British Soap Award for Best Comedy Performance (2011, 2013 and 2016).
